{"id":782,"date":"2019-10-05T12:27:30","date_gmt":"2019-10-05T09:27:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/?page_id=782"},"modified":"2019-10-05T12:31:40","modified_gmt":"2019-10-05T09:31:40","slug":"cevre-is-sagligi-ve-guvenligi-kalite-politikasi","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/cevre-is-sagligi-ve-guvenligi-kalite-politikasi\/","title":{"rendered":"\u00c7evre\/\u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi Kalite Politikas\u0131"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3><\/h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>\u00c7EVRE\/\u0130\u015e SA\u011eLI\u011eI VE G\u00dcVENL\u0130\u011e\u0130 KAL\u0130TE POL\u0130T\u0130KASI<\/h3>\n<p><strong>Hizmet faaliyetlerini ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirirken;<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u00c7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131n, ziyaret\u00e7ilerimizin, m\u00fc\u015fterilerimizin, \u00e7evremizin refah, sa\u011fl\u0131k ve g\u00fcvenlik ihtiya\u00e7lar\u0131n\u0131 m\u00fcmk\u00fcn olan en \u00fcst d\u00fczeyde kar\u015f\u0131layabilmek i\u00e7in ;<\/p>\n<hr class=\"no_line\" style=\"margin: 0 auto 10px auto\"\/>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi \/ \u00c7evre Y\u00f6netim Sistemini kurmay\u0131, s\u00fcrd\u00fcrmeyi ve s\u00fcrekli geli\u015ftirmeyi<\/li>\n<li>\u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi \/ \u00c7evre konusundaki performans\u0131m\u0131z\u0131 en \u00fcst d\u00fczeye getirmeyi,<\/li>\n<li>T\u00fcm \u00e7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131m\u0131zla birlikte beceri, tecr\u00fcbe ve bilgilerimizi s\u00fcrekli art\u0131rabilmek i\u00e7in e\u011fitimler ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirmeyi,<\/li>\n<li>Ta\u015feronlar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131, birlikte \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z tedarik\u00e7ileri ve ziyaret\u00e7ilerimizi \u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi \/ \u00c7evre Y\u00f6netim Sistemimiz hakk\u0131nda bilgilendirerek bu konudaki uyumumuzu artt\u0131rmay\u0131,<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7evreye verdi\u011fimiz etkileri minimum d\u00fczeye indirerek kirlenmenin \u00f6nlenmesini sa\u011flamay\u0131,<\/li>\n<li>\u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi ile ilgili kazalar\u0131n, meslek hastal\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n ve zarar\u0131n olu\u015fmas\u0131n\u0131 engellemeyi,<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0130\u015f Sa\u011fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve G\u00fcvenli\u011fi \/ \u00c7evre ile ilgili ulusal mevzuata, \u00e7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131z m\u00fc\u015fterilerin s\u00f6zle\u015fmede belirtilen \u00f6zel gereklere uymay\u0131,<\/p>\n<p><strong>Taahh\u00fct etmi\u015ftir.<\/strong><br \/>\n<strong>Bu do\u011frultuda ama\u00e7 ve hedeflerimiz belirlenecek ve izlenecektir.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; \u00c7EVRE\/\u0130\u015e SA\u011eLI\u011eI VE G\u00dcVENL\u0130\u011e\u0130 KAL\u0130TE POL\u0130T\u0130KASI Hizmet faaliyetlerini ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirirken; \u00c7al\u0131\u015fanlar\u0131m\u0131z\u0131n, ziyaret\u00e7ilerimizin, m\u00fc\u015fterilerimizin, \u00e7evremizin refah, sa\u011fl\u0131k ve g\u00fcvenlik ihtiya\u00e7lar\u0131n\u0131 m\u00fcmk\u00fcn olan en \u00fcst d\u00fczeyde kar\u015f\u0131layabilmek i\u00e7in<span class=\"excerpt-hellip\"> [\u2026]<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-782","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/782"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=782"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/teknikistif.com\/w